ENTRY            30069   20260401   20260528   20260528       3223
SUBENT        30069001   20260401   20260528   20260528       3223
BIB                 11         22
TITLE       Applicability of the statistical model for explaining
            the ratio of the (n,n')/(n,2n) cross-sections
AUTHOR     (G.Peto, P.Bornemisza-Pauspertl, J.Karolyi)
INSTITUTE  (3HUNKOS,3HUNDEB)
REFERENCE  (J,AHP,25,91,1968)
FACILITY   (CCW,3HUNDEB) 300 keV locally built Cascade generator
INC-SOURCE (D-T) d+t reaction
DETECTOR   (NAICR) NaI(Tl) Spectrometer for gamma detection.
           Flux monitored from pulses due to gammas of over 2 MeV
METHOD     (ACTIV)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Errors given are due to standard cross-
           section errors, gamma detection errors and statistics
STATUS     (APRVD) approved by Peto (1972-09-05)
           (TABLE,,G.Peto+,J,AHP,25,91,1968) Table 1
HISTORY    (19690717C)
           (19720925A) CA. Status approved added +
                         data-err corrected in subentry 5.
           (19930316A) HW.- Reaction code altered in subent 005,
           obsolete keywords/codes converted/deleted.-
           (20080305A) BIB section updated
           (20210930A) VS. REACTION code corrected in 003.
           (20260401A) VT. Entry revised
ENDBIB              22
COMMON               2          3
EN         EN-RSL-HW
MEV        MEV
15.0       0.3
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           29
SUBENT        30069002   20260401   20260528   20260528       3223
BIB                  6         11
REACTION   (39-Y-89(N,INL)39-Y-89-M,,SIG)
           Half-life measured as 17.0 +/- 0.6 Sec
DECAY-DATA (39-Y-89-M,,DG,915.)
MONITOR    (59-PR-141(N,2N)59-PR-140,,SIG)
SAMPLE     Y2O3 (yttrium oxide)
COMMENT    Statistical model calculation yields a ratio
                                        (n,n')/(n,2n) = 0.411
